[SN]TITLE[SN]
Inverness man convicted of serious sexual offences

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An Inverness man has been convicted of a series of serious sexual offences against children

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Robert McGregor pleaded guilty to a total of 41 offences at the High Court in Edinburgh.
Police Scotland has described his actions as "abhorrent" and "unforgivable", and praised the courage shown by his victims.
McGregor is expected to appear at the High Court in Edinburgh again next month for sentencing.
